--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Job description 1 : 
Collaborate with stakeholders to gather and understand business or product requirements.
Translate those requirements into structured AI prompts, workflows, or automation solutions.
Craft, test, and iterate prompts to achieve high-quality and consistent outputs.
Evaluate and recommend the best AI tools/models for different use cases.
Build reusable prompt templates and knowledge bases for internal teams.
Stay up to date with the latest in AI tools, models, and prompting techniques.
Document solutions, prompts, and best practices for scalability and reuse.
Collaborate with devs, designers, and product teams for AI integration.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 2 : 
To build and scale effective use of AI tools is crucial for our long-term data strategy. You will help define and implement prompt engineering standards, making AI a productive collaborator across departments.
Understand internal stakeholders' needs related to AI and data usage, and translate them into effective prompt strategies.
Design, test, and optimize prompts for LLMs (e.g., ChatGPT, Gemini).
Develop reusable prompt chains and templates that standardize interactions with AI.
Monitor prompt performance and iterate based on output quality and user feedback.
Collaborate with data professionals to integrate LLMs into reporting, analysis, and automation pipelines.
Stay up to date on best practices and advancements in the prompt engineering space.
Promote ethical use and governance of generative AI internally.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 3 : 
Strong understanding of how LLMs work and experience using tools like ChatGPT, Claude, or Gemini.
Basic programming skills (Python preferred) and understanding of API usage.
Analytical mindset and ability to assess model responses critically.
Excellent written communication in English; ability to write clear, effective prompts.
A proactive and experimental mindset, willing to test and iterate rapidly.
Demonstrated ability to work independently and handle ownership of tasks.
Strong collaboration skills with both technical and non-technical teams.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 4 : 
We are seeking a highly detail-oriented and creative AI Prompt Engineer to join our team and play a key role in designing and refining AI prompts that generate high-quality clinical summary reports and other content derived from complex medical data sources. 
This role will be instrumental in shaping the interaction between large language models (LLMs) and our healthcare-specific workflows, ensuring that generated content is accurate, relevant, and aligned with business needs.
Key Responsibilities:
Develop, test, and optimize prompts for AI models to generate clinical summary reports and support emerging healthcare use cases.
Analyze various data inputs, including structured and unstructured clinical documents, to understand context and create effective prompt strategies.
Continuously learn and adapt to the specific clinical processes and documentation standards used within the organization.
Iterate and refine prompts based on output quality, model behavior, and feedback from clinical stakeholders.
Collaborate with clinical informatics teams, data scientists, and software engineers to integrate prompt workflows into production environments.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 5 :
Proven experience working with LLMs (e.g., GPT-4, Claude, etc.) in a prompt engineering or content generation capacity.
Strong understanding of natural language processing (NLP) and language model behavior.
Ability to interpret clinical content and healthcare data is highly desirable.
Exceptional attention to detail and a continuous improvement mindset.
Excellent communication and collaboration skills.
Background in healthcare, life sciences, or medical documentation is a plus.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 6 : 
Prompt Development: Design and refine client-specific prompts, ensuring accuracy and relevance. Define tool descriptions for agentic frameworks to enhance AI interactions.
Optimization & Testing: Improve prompts for clarity and performance, automate testing with scripts, and evaluate LLMs for best-fit solutions.
Evaluation & Benchmarking: Develop evaluation frameworks and benchmark prompts to establish best practices.
Collaboration & Documentation: Work with Customer Success and Data Science teams, maintaining clear documentation on prompt development and optimization.
Research & Innovation: Stay updated on NLP advancements, experiment with new prompting strategies, and refine model-specific adaptations.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 7 : 
Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Computer Science, Data Science, Linguistics, or a related field.
Strong understanding of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning principles.
Experience with AI prompt engineering, including writing, optimizing, and evaluating prompts.
Proficiency in programming languages such as Python.
Familiarity with AI frameworks and libraries (e.g., TensorFlow, PyTorch, Hugging Face).
Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills.
Strong written and verbal communication skills.
Ability to work collaboratively in a team environment and manage multiple projects simultaneously.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 8 : 
Experience with large language models (e.g., GPT-3, GPT-4, Llama3) and their applications.
Knowledge of data visualization tools and techniques.
Background in linguistics or computational linguistics.
Experience with agile development methodologies.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 9 : 
AI and NLP AI models and Python skills
Expertise in Prompt Engineering having worked on GPT4 and other variants of GPT
Developing testing and refining AI generated text prompts
Collaborating with content product and data teams to align prompts with the customer's needs
Continuously improving prompt quality performance and the overall AI prompt generation process
Prompt tuning in context Learning Prompt modification.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 10 : 
Design and develop prompt solutions based on clients' requirements.
Implement and integrate prompt systems with existing infrastructure.
Perform prompt testing and quality assurance.
Troubleshoot and resolve prompt issues.
Maintain documentation of prompt configurations, changes, and incidents.
Stay up-to-date with the latest prompt technologies and best practices.
Collaborate with clients and stakeholders to gather requirements and provide technical guidance.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 11 : 
3-5 years of experience as a Prompt Engineer or similar role.
Experience with prompt software and systems.
Strong knowledge of prompt technologies and best practices.
Proficient in prompt design, implementation, and testing.
Strong troubleshooting and problem-solving skills.
Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.
Ability to work well in a team and collaborate effectively with stakeholders.
Bachelor's degree in a relevant field such as Computer Science or Software Engineering.
Relevant certifications in prompt technologies are preferred.

